#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:953 input:953 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Dient als basis voor overzeese kolonisatie en handel. Hier kun je ook je "
"soldaten, goederen en gereedschappen opslaan."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew warehouse: Port
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:955 input:955 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Similar to the Headquarters a Port can be attacked and destroyed by an "
"enemy. It is recommendable to send soldiers to defend it."
msgstr ""
"Net als het hoofdkwartier kan een Haven worden aangevallen en vernietigd "
"door een vijand. Het is aan te raden om soldaten te sturen om het te "
"verdedigen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:964 input:964 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'For there is hope for a tree, if it be cut down, that it will sprout again, "
"and that its shoots will not cease.'"
msgstr ""
"'Want er is hoop voor een boom, als hij wordt omgehakt, dat hij weer zal "
"uitlopen en dat zijn scheuten niet zullen ophouden.'"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:966 input:966 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Book of Job"
msgstr "Boek Job"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:968 input:968 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Collects fallen branches from trees in the vicinity. The trees are not "
"harmed."
msgstr ""
"Verzamelt afgebroken takken van bomen in de omgeving. De bomen worden niet "
"beschadigd."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:970 input:970 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Branches are the primary building material and fuel. The branch collector "
"needs trees nearby."
msgstr ""
"Takken zijn het belangrijkste bouwmateriaal en brandstof. De "
"takkenverzamelaar heeft bomen in de buurt nodig."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:977 input:977 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Cast your net on the right side of the boat and you will find some.'"
msgstr ""
"'Gooi je net aan de rechterkant van de boot uit en je zult er een paar "
"vinden.'"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:979 input:979 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Gospel of John"
msgstr "Evangelie van Johannes"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:981 input:981 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Catches fish in the nearby waters."
msgstr "Vist in de nabijgelegen wateren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:983 input:983 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "The fisher needs water nearby to catch fish."
msgstr "De visser heeft water in de buurt nodig om vis te kunnen vangen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:990 input:990 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'The Lord is my shepherd, I shall not want.'"
msgstr "'De Heer is mijn herder, mij zal niets ontbreken.'"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:992 input:992 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Psalm 23"
msgstr "Psalm 23"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Shepherd's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:994 input:994 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Raises sheep for wool, meat and fur."
msgstr "Houdt schapen voor wol, vlees en vacht."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Well
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1001 input:1001 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Then Israel sang this song: Spring up, O well!'"
msgstr "'Toen zong Israël dit lied: Spring op, O bron!'"

