#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Brick Kiln
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1040 input:1040 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Burns clay and branches into bricks, which are used as granite for "
"construction."
msgstr ""
"Brandt klei en takken tot bakstenen, die worden gebruikt als graniet voor de "
"bouw."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Clearing Tent
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1047 input:1047 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'Clear the way for the people; build up the highway, remove the stones.'"
msgstr ""
"'Maak de weg vrij voor het volk; leg de snelweg aan, verwijder de stenen.'"

